ys-recommend-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":33042,"position":3},"title":"Fudayl on Forgiveness: Always recommend mercy and forbearance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"'Abdu Samad reported: Al-Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf a man comes to you complaining about another man, then say: O brother, forgive him, as forgiveness is closer to righteousness. If he says my heart cannot tolerate forgiveness, but rather retaliation as Allah Almighty has\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9781,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/11\/prophet-forbearing-forgiving\/","url_meta":{"origin":33042,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: The Prophet was forbearing, forgiving","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was not presented with two matters but that he would choose the easier of them, as long as it was not sinful. If it was sinful, he would be the furthest of people from it. The Prophet did\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18326,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/01\/forgiveness-better-than-revenge\/","url_meta":{"origin":33042,"position":5},"title":"Ibn al-Qayyim on Mercy: Forgiveness more beloved to Allah than revenge","author":"Abu Amina Elias",